en_764212_0	Air Vice Marshal H.M.S.K.B Kotakadeniya, Vice Chancellor at Kotelawala Defence University (KDU) paid a courtesy call on the Commander of the Army Lieutenant General Shavendra Silva on Friday (4) at his office in the Army Headquarters.
en_764212_1	During this discussion, both of them shared views on general matters of training with special focus on KDU degree courses and modules, related to military career, etc. The visiting VC also extended his best wishes on the new office of Lieutenant General Silva.
en_764212_2	At the end of the interaction, both of them exchanged mementos as symbols of goodwill.
